creator: East African Community
descriptionHtml: EACPass is the only Digital Covid 19 Certificate Mobile app that accepted by East African Community (EAC). With EACPass Mobile App, traveler has verifiable way to document their health status such as record of a COVID PCR test or vaccination administered in within EAC countries.
descriptionShort: EACPass is the only Digital Covid 19 Certificate Mobile app
